  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The planet Earth has been attacked by Cthulhu</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only ones who can protect us are our beloved cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as your favorite pet, arm yourself with yarns, fruits and other delicacies. Dress up in the most stylish outfit possible and show Cthulhu why cats rule the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dozen of cats to choose from</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every cat has unique attributes. Recognize their strengths and weaknesses and adjust your build accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy yourself something comfortable and powerful</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Increase your attack speed, improve your durability or unleash the power of the rainbow! Upgrades, People, Upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Injection of Love</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eat your weapons to gain permanent buffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meta-Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While fighting Cthulhu you collect cardboards, which you can then use to buy new cats or arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The planet Earth has been attacked by Cthulhu</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only ones who can protect us are our beloved cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as your favorite pet, arm yourself with yarns, fruits and other delicacies. Dress up in the most stylish outfit possible and show Cthulhu why cats rule the world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dozen of cats to choose from</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every cat has unique attributes. Recognize their strengths and weaknesses and adjust your build accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy yourself something comfortable and powerful</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Increase your attack speed, improve your durability or unleash the power of the rainbow! Upgrades, People, Upgrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://s